snippet.title: The Sims 4 Movie Hangout Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Invite your friends over for a movie night and hangout in carefree style with The Sims 4 Movie Hangout Stuff!
 
Learn more about this Stuff Pack:  http://o.ea.com/50563
 
Pop a bowl of popcorn, gather around the projector screen, and entertain your Sims with a variety of movies. Embrace a low-key mood by dressing your Sims in boho-chic fashion and effortless hairstyles.
